  "industry_note": "AISI D2 / DIN 1.2379 / X153CrMoV12 / JIS SKD11 / KS STD11 — high-Cr (~12%) high-C (1.5%) cold-work tool steel. Excellent wear / dimensional stability. Applications: stamping / blanking die (auto body panel), slitter knife, thread-rolling die, cold-header punch, knife blade. Commercial brands: Bohler K110, Uddeholm Sverker 21, Hitachi SLD.",
